Write a program to analyse how slight variations in the denominator coefficients affect the pole locations. 
Use D(z)=z2+a1z+a2 where a1=âˆ’1.2 and a2=0.72. Vary a1 from -1.5 to -0.9 in steps of 0.1 and plot the poles for each case on the same diagram. Discuss how the stability of the system changes with variations in a1.

clc; clear; clf;
